# Direct (top-level) dependencies only. Transitive deps are resolved and pinned
# into requirements.txt by pip-tools:
#
#   pip install pip-tools
#   pip-compile requirements.in -o requirements.txt
#
# Versions are pinned to the current known-good stack. Relax them deliberately
# (e.g. drop the ==) when you actually want to upgrade, then re-run pip-compile.

